graph TB
    subgraph "Model Registry Operator"
        Controller[controller-manager<br/>Deployment]
        Webhook[webhook-service<br/>Admission Webhooks]
        Metrics[controller-manager-metrics-service<br/>Prometheus Metrics]

        Controller -->|validates/mutates| Webhook
        Controller -->|exposes| Metrics
    end

    subgraph "Model Registry Instance (per CR)"
        RestContainer[REST Container<br/>8080/TCP]
        OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]
        Service[model-registry Service<br/>ClusterIP]
        Route[OpenShift Route<br/>External Access]

        OAuthProxy -->|forwards to| RestContainer
        Service -->|routes to| OAuthProxy
        Service -->|routes to| RestContainer
        Route -->|exposes| Service
    end

    User[Data Scientist] -->|creates| ModelRegistryCR[ModelRegistry CR<br/>v1beta1]
    ModelRegistryCR -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|creates| RestContainer
    Controller -->|creates| OAuthProxy
    Controller -->|creates| Service
    Controller -->|creates| Route
    Controller -->|creates| ServiceAccount[Service Account<br/>RBAC]
    Controller -->|creates| NetworkPolicy[Network Policy]

    RestContainer -->|connects to| PostgreSQL[(PostgreSQL/MySQL<br/>5432/3306)]
    OAuthProxy -->|authenticates via| OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]

    Controller -->|reconciles via| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]

    Controller -->|integrates with| Platform[opendatahub-operator<br/>components.platform.opendatahub.io]

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Metrics fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style RestContainer fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OAuthProxy fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ModelRegistryCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style PostgreSQL fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OAuthServer fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Platform fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
